<div class="story"> <p>Southern Woods is the first subdivision you hit when you come across the Wright Memorial Bridge into Kitty Hawk. Located on The Woods Road in the middle of <a href="http://www.nccoastalreserve.net/web/crp/kitty-hawk-woods" title="Kitty Hawk Woods">Kitty Hawk Woods</a>, the community of Southern Woods is ideal for someone looking to commute to Virginia for work. You will find Southern Woods just across from <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/southern-shores/" title="Southern Shores">Southern Shores</a> and just past the subdivision of <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/seascape.asp" title="Sea Scape">Sea Scape</a>.</p>  <p><a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/southern-woods-covenants-1.pdf" title="Southern Woods covenants phase 1" target="_blank">Southern Woods covenants phase 1</a> & <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/outer banks/real estate/KittyHawk/southern-woods-covenants.pdf" title="Southern Woods covenants phase 2" target="_blank">Southern Woods covenants phase 2</a>   - - - <a href="https://www.outerbankshome.com/Covenant-Disclaimer.asp" target="_blank"><b>    *</b></a></p>
